# Cursor Setup

## Step 1 — Open Cursor Settings

Go to:

``` id="5mjlwm"
Cursor → Settings → Models
```

Enable:

``` id="wfr13o"
OpenAI Compatible API
```

---

## Step 2 — Configure API

Use:

```json
{
  "apiKey": "YOUR_API_KEY",
  "baseURL": "https://platform.nanobridge.net/v1",
  "model": "deepseek-v4-pro"
}
```

